              <strong>Winter pilgrim note:</strong> Very few pilgrims walk the Coastal Route in winter due to the reduced ferry service. If you plan a winter Camino, consider the Portuguese Interior Route (via Tui/Valença) as a more reliable alternative — the Valença–Tui bridge operates 24/7 and is always accessible on foot. See the overland alternative section below for details.
